Katherine Woodville (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katherine_Woodville_(actress) 0 Katherine Woodville (born Catherine Woodville; 4 December 1938 – 5 June 2013) was an English film and television actress. She changed her professional name to Kate Woodville in 1967 upon moving to the US, where she would eventually become a life member of the Actors Studio.
